videos.headline: Freiermuth's 17-yard TD catch puts Penn State on the board
videos.description: Sean Clifford hits Pat Freiermuth with a 17-yard touchdown pass to give Penn State a 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Freiermuth’s 17-yard TD catch puts Penn State on the board) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clifford dives into end zone to pad Penn State's lead
videos.description: Penn State QB Sean Clifford fakes the handoff then runs for a two-yard touchdown to increase Penn State's lead over Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clifford dives into end zone to pad Penn State’s lead) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State turns INT into TD
videos.description: Tariq Castro-Fields intercepts Shea Patterson to set up Sean Clifford's 25-yard touchdown pass to KJ Hamler and put Penn State up three scores.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State turns INT into TD) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charbonnet's run puts Michigan on the board
videos.description: Zach Charbonnet runs for a 12-yard touchdown to cut Penn State's lead to 21-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Charbonnet’s run puts Michigan on the board) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charbonnet runs in 2nd TD
videos.description: Michigan's Zach Charbonnet scores a 12-yard rushing touchdown to put Michigan within striking distance of Penn State.

videos.headline: Clifford unleashes 53-yard TD pass to Hamler
videos.description: Sean Clifford finds KJ Hamler again, this time for a 53-yard touchdown to increase Penn State's lead to 28-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clifford unleashes 53-yard TD pass to Hamler) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan's play ruled TD after long review
videos.description: Michigan runs a QB sneak from the 1 and officials rule it a touchdown after a long delay to pull players out of the pile.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan’s play ruled TD after long review) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State stops Michigan on 4th-and-goal
videos.description: Shea Patterson's pass attempt goes through Ronnie Bell's hands as Penn State's defense pours on the pressure and stops Michigan on 4th-and-goal.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State stops Michigan on 4th-and-goal) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State holds off Michigan for dramatic win
videos.description: After nearly losing a three-touchdown lead, Penn State is able to hold on to beat Michigan 28-21.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Penn State holds off Michigan for dramatic win) 2019/10/19 ESHEET SOTFULL
